[Course_Description]
If you don’t have access to low-interest financing for your business, you’re taking big risks and missing golden opportunities. Having access to credit will give your business a safety net to protect against short-term cash flow problems and help to secure your future. This course arms you with 12+ financing options and teaches you exactly how to apply for and unlock each one. Learn how to use a prefinancing checklist to prepare your business for capital hunting, how to leverage the three most common small business financing methods, and how to get the best loan terms using the U.S. Small Business Administration (SBA). Plus, learn about nontraditional sources of financing for startups, such as personal loans, venture funding, and even plastic financing on your credit card. If you’re ready to leverage debt like the world’s top-tier businesses, take this course today and get the financing that will make you the leader in your market. This course was created by WealthFit. We are pleased to host this content in our library.